Install Lyris as a gem in Rails > 3 Apps

1. Create "lyris" directory under vendor/gems

2. Add gem 'lyris', '0.9.1', :to => "vendor/gems"

3. clone this repository in 'vendor/gems/lyris'

4. bundle install

5. Restart App and it should be working. If you are getting an error about Nokogiri then add:
 gem 'nokogiri' in your Gemfile.